      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TWIN FIN (1) is a fast beginner but out of character last time when always well back and missed the placings, finishing fourth (27.98) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Placed the start prior (27.98) at this track after firing out of the boxes. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Key runner on her best form. BILLY ME GOAT (2) had been in great form but missed the frame latest when sixth (28.21) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Generally fast to begin but was always well back despite the low draw last time. Form here at the trip sound including six wins. Has won three of five starts from this draw. Worth another chance. RIGATONI MONELLI (3) gave a start after copping a check in running and missed the frame when a 10 length eighth (28.38) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Better than last start and can bounce back. RUSTY ROCKET (8) was in the money last start and wasn't beaten far - poses a threat again.",
